    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>海亚世界 EA2.0 大型版本更新！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299030/extras/71568d3a6530332ba4e093ee7232e05e.avif?t=1747991749\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >耗时了一年之多！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们修改了游戏许多机制，画面大幅强化，增加了更多有趣的玩法！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎来到海亚世界！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是个冒险x创建的RPG！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挖掘、建造、战斗、冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打怪练等，破坏地形并采集素材建立据点！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >王国面临了魔物的攻击！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险者为了拯救王国，前往探索远古大陆，寻找未解之谜！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299030/extras/e8f846a1942e2fd7540a380691692ac8.avif?t=1747991749\" width=800 height=374 /></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索未知的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>远古之地</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个被遗忘的古大陆，冒险者为了调查魔物异常而前往冒险，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这可以任意破坏地貌与建造来探索这个未知的地区。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>纳鲁斯大陆</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险者的故乡，海亚居民主要生活的大陆，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有着许多繁荣的城镇与居民，可以前往此地方与居民的交流！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299030/extras/417cd4f772a928257aa888d80ad7915a.avif?t=1747991749\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>各式各样的武器、装备与技能</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15种以上战斗风格的武器类型</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﹝盾剑、大剑、斧头﹞</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﹝长枪、双剑、利刃、太刀、拳套﹞</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﹝短弓、短杖、长弓、长杖、圣书、双弩﹞</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﹝手枪、霰弹枪、狙击枪、突击步枪﹞</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100件以上的独特武器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100件以上的装备类型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >200种独特的技能招式</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更加好上手的战斗系统，随时切换不同风格的武器来对抗敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299030/extras/5d4016eb9daac78179f24e0139598db9.avif?t=1747991749\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与强大的敌人战斗，并获得战利品吧！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海亚世界有许多强大的敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级等级并强化装备来挑战他们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们身上可以有许多丰富的奖励品喔！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299030/extras/be41db4d68a03bcdb0cc4ec712225d00.avif?t=1747991749\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>丰富且华丽的百变时装</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上万种时装搭配，让角色更加闪耀！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299030/extras/980d6b940afdff2281b7e3ee2693ced7.avif?t=1747991749\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与NPC同伴一起冒险</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险不孤单，可以与30位以上独特伙伴一同冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可爱萌宠，能蒐集10种以上的宠物陪伴着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299030/extras/f2672554f91470175b3a1a573c70663d.avif?t=1747991749\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>更多充满乐趣的系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >载具-搭乘载具探索辽阔的世界，20种风格载具供你使用！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >钓鱼-化身天才小钓手，能钓到50种以上的鱼类！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >农耕-自给自足，能够在据点耕作种田！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299030/extras/6dfb9c9886e8b29f09b94dd846090ae2.avif?t=1747991749\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>控制器支援</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以使用Xbox控制器畅玩，不需要额外的设定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也可以使用SteamDeck来游玩海亚世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299030/extras/4ccaa642352054c424765d1191a53fd8.avif?t=1747991749\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>连线游玩</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以使用Steam的连线功能与朋友一起游玩~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一起冒险一起创造！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一同打造属于你们的海亚世界吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299030/extras/b06c08eddc4ff2033f93e5b6e6fd5fac.avif?t=1747991749\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p>",
